<div class="row">
	<div class="large-11 small-11 columns small-centered">
		<h3>PURPOSE OF THIS NEWSLETTER</h3>
		<h4>The purpose of this newsletter is to deliver the best content, news and devlopements each week in a way that is useful and clear to both casual and everday followers. There are three goals as of now for the newsletter. The first goal is to provide a balanced view of Bitcoin. In doing so the newsletteer will consist of economic, technical, social and other perspectives. The second goal is to help people understand Bitcoin a little better every week and begin to understand its potential as a currency and beyond. The last goal is to highlight bitcoin related companies, products, services, projects and merchants. The hope is to make bitcion more accessible and well understood by a much wider audience. We will work to find a newsletter format that works best to meet these goals based on feedback from the community.</h4>
